# Chatbot Frontend (React + Vite)

A simple chatbot frontend built using React, Vite, and plain CSS — integrated with a backend that supports `/chat` and `/sse` endpoints.

---

## 🚀 Features

- React + Vite for fast development
- Plain CSS styling (no frameworks)
- Textarea input + "Send" button
- Integration with `/chat` API (POST)
- Live message streaming via `/sse` (Server-Sent Events)

---

## 🛠️ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the project

```bash
cd frontend

npm install

npm run dev
